<P>A Complete Collection OF ALL THE LAVVS OF VIRGINIA NOW IN FORCE.</P>
<P>Carefully Copied from the ASSEMBLY RECORDS.</P>
<P>To which is Annexed an ALPHABETICAL TABLE.</P>
<P><HI>LONDON,</HI> Printed by <HI>T. J.</HI> for <HI>J. P.</HI> and are to be &s;old by <HI>Tho. Mercer</HI> at the Sign of the <HI>Half Moon</HI> the Corner Shop of the <HI>Royal-Exchange</HI> in <HI>Cornhil.</HI></P>
