<P>BE it enacted by the Kings mo&s;t Excellent Maje&s;ty, by and with the con&s;ent of the General A&s;&s;em|bly, and it is hereby enacted, that Tho&s;e Additional
<PB N="279" REF="153"> Fees hereafter &s;et down, over and be&s;ides the fees nomi|nated in the Printed Book, be demanded and taken by County-court Clerks, as ju&s;t fees, and none other, <HI>viz.</HI></P>
