<DIV1 TYPE="index">
<PB REF="164">
<HEAD>AN ALPHABETICAL TABLE</HEAD>
<DIV2 N="A" TYPE="part">
<HEAD>A</HEAD>
<DIV3 TYPE="section">
<HEAD>Accounts.</HEAD>
<LIST>
<ITEM><HI>ACcounts</HI> again&s;t Dead Mens E|&s;tates, <HI>Page. 70.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM>Ballancing <HI>Accounts</HI> of Decea&s;ed Per&s;ons, <HI>ibid.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Accounts</HI> again&s;t Dead Mens E&s;tates, &s;hall be admitted in Di&s;count; <HI>Page. 71.</HI></ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Accounts</HI> &s;hall not be pleadable after Three years by per&s;ons living in the Country, <HI>Page. 179.</HI></ITEM>
</LIST>
</DIV3>
<DIV3 TYPE="section">
<HEAD>Actions and Arre&s;ts.</HEAD>
<LIST>
